Package: razimuth
Title: VHF Transmitter Location Estimation
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Christopher", "Peck", email = "christopher.p.peck@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Very high frequency (VHF) transmitter location estimation using the azimuthal telemetry model (ATM) presented in the paper entitled: Accounting for location uncertainty in azimuthal telemetry data improves ecological inference by Gerber et al (in review).
